    <item>
      <title>汉莎航空为头等舱配备铅块以平衡客舱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/lufthansa-fits-jets-with-lead-weight-to-balance-out-first-class</link>
      <description><![CDATA[航空工程师们花了近一个世纪的时间试图减轻飞机重量以节省燃料。德国汉莎航空公司现在正在对部分飞机采取相反的做法，以便让头等舱乘客晚上能睡个好觉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/lufthansa-fits-jets-with-lead-weight-to-balance-out-first-class</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
